narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend taking L3 and L4 separately for any student who has that opportunity. I think Italian 145 tries to put too much into too little time
DO NOT DO THIS TO YOURSELF. You will honestly regret it.

Don't take this class. It's much more intensive than 125, and significantly less enjoyable. One of the few things that got me up in the morning to go to this class was the idea of going to Italy this summer, but I'm still really not sure if it was worth it. I think I must have learned a lot based on the amount of work we had, which hopefully will prove true in the future, but right now I just feel very burned out.
